  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Gill's Exposition of the Entire Bible",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "A noise shall come up even to the ends of the earth,.... Wars, and rumours of wars, everywhere, till the cup has gone round, and all nations have drank of it, and have felt the power of divine wrath for their sins: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "for the Lord hath a controversy with the nations; will enter into a judicial process with them; will litigate the point with them, and try it openly; that it may be seen who is in the right, and who in the wrong: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "he will plead with all flesh; or enter into judgment with them, as Kimchi; or reprove them in judgment, as Jarchi; he will be too many for them; he will carry his case, overcome them in judgment, and reprove and condemn them. Or the words may be rendered, \"he will be judged by all flesh\" (s); he will submit it to the judgment of the whole world, if it is not a righteous thing in him to do what he is about to do, and will do; he will make it clear and manifest that he does nothing unjustly, but all according to the strict rules of justice and equity: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "he will give them that are wicked to the sword, saith the Lord; to be destroyed by it, and none but them; and seeing they are such that deserve it, he is not to be charged with unrighteousness in so doing. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "(s)    \"judicium subibit ipse cum omni carne\", Tigurine version. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(s)    \"judicium subibit ipse cum omni carne\", Tigurine version. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
